    <summary><span data-ttu-id="3e095-101">指定可用的值以指出對合約所要求或支援的可靠工作階段所提供的支援。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3e095-101">Specifies the values available to indicate the support for reliable sessions that a contract requires or supports.</span></span></summary>
    <remarks>
      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="3e095-102">您可以使用 <xref:System.ServiceModel.SessionMode> 列舉 (包含 <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceContractAttribute.SessionMode%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> 屬性) 來要求、允許或禁止繫結使用連接至或支援服務合約的端點之間的工作階段。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3e095-102">Use the <xref:System.ServiceModel.SessionMode> enumeration with the <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceContractAttribute.SessionMode%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property to require, allow, or prohibit bindings to use sessions between endpoints that connect to or support the service contract.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3e095-103">工作階段是一種將兩個 (或更多) 端點間所交換的一組訊息予以關聯的方式。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3e095-103">A session is a way of correlating a set of messages exchanged between two or more endpoints.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3e095-104">如需有關工作階段的詳細資訊，請參閱[使用工作階段的](~/docs/framework/wcf/using-sessions.md)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3e095-104">For more information about sessions, see [Using Sessions](~/docs/framework/wcf/using-sessions.md).</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="3e095-105">如果您的服務支援工作階段，便可使用 <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceBehaviorAttribute.InstanceContextMode%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> 屬性，來指定您的服務合約實作之執行個體與通道工作階段間的關係。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3e095-105">If your service supports sessions, you can then use the <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceBehaviorAttribute.InstanceContextMode%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property to specify the relationship between instances of your service contract implementation and the channel session.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="3e095-106">比方說，如果<xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceContractAttribute.SessionMode%2A>屬性設定為允許，<xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceBehaviorAttribute.InstanceContextMode%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>屬性設定為<xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContextMode?displayProperty=nameWithType>，用戶端可以使用支援對相同的服務物件進行重複的呼叫的可靠工作階段的繫結。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3e095-106">For example, if the <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceContractAttribute.SessionMode%2A> property is set to Allowed and the <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceBehaviorAttribute.InstanceContextMode%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property is set to <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContextMode?displayProperty=nameWithType>, a client can use a binding that supports reliable sessions to make repeated calls to the same service object.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="3e095-107">由於工作階段是應用程式模型使用的通道層級概念，在合約的 <xref:System.ServiceModel.SessionMode> 列舉與 <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceBehaviorAttribute.InstanceContextMode%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> 屬性之間會有互動行為，以控制通道與特定服務物件的關聯。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3e095-107">Because a session is a channel-level concept that the application model uses, there is an interaction between the <xref:System.ServiceModel.SessionMode> enumeration in a contract and the <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceBehaviorAttribute.InstanceContextMode%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property, which controls the association between channels and specific service objects.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="3e095-108">下表根據服務的 <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceContractAttribute.SessionMode%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> 屬性與 <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceBehaviorAttribute.InstanceContextMode%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> 屬性等值的組合，說明支援可靠工作階段或不支援可靠工作階段之傳入通道的結果。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3e095-108">The following table shows the result of an incoming channel either supporting reliable sessions or not supporting reliable sessions given a service's combination of the values of the <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceContractAttribute.SessionMode%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property and the <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceBehaviorAttribute.InstanceContextMode%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property.</span></span>  
  
